    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4667327/" class="title-link">明白情绪的根本源头</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4667327"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/candyhyq/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u3223898-6.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/candyhyq/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">Candy</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-02-22"
      class="main-meta">2011-02-22 10:14:45</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4667327_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  了解到情绪的源头就是这么一个气血小点。这段时间佛书、心灵类的书看了一大堆，反而越看越云里雾里了。看了这本书，妨若射进了一丝阳光。脑子已经装进不少道理圣经了，重要的是好好修这心。心即是气。不着相、不住心地看待这黄庭之气。

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/4667327/#comments">(1回应)</a>
